In internal/logrender/interleaved_test.go, the expectContains helper (lines ~256-263) is a thin wrapper around strings.Contains + t.Errorf. It has 21 call sites. Inline it: replace each expectContains(t, got, expected) call with a direct if-check using strings.Contains, or adopt a concise pattern like:

  if !strings.Contains(got, substr) { t.Errorf(...) }

Delete the expectContains function definition after all call sites are updated.
